s.\",\n244:         \"Map status/navigation bar styling intent into HarmonyOS page/theme composition where available.\"\n245:       ]\n246:     },\n247:     {\n248:       \"assetType\": \"drawables-and-images\",\n249:       \"sourcePaths\": [\n250:         \"app/src/main/res/drawable\",\n251:         \"app/src/main/res/mipmap*\",\n252:         \"app/src/main/assets\",\n253:         \"README.md screenshots and demo references\"\n254:       ],\n255:       \"targetPaths\": [\n256:         \"entry/src/main/resources/base/media\"\n257:       ],\n258:       \"rules\": [\n259:         \"Copy raster assets directly when valid.\",\n260:         \"Convert icon/vector/state resources into HarmonyOS-friendly media or state code without losing semantic role.\"\n261:       ]\n262:     }\n263:   ],\n264:   \"dependencies\": [\n265:     {\n266:       \"sourceDependency\": \"androidx.navigation:navigation-compose\",\n267:       \"replacementStrategy\": \"Use current HarmonyOS route/page shell under `app/` and feature pages instead of Android Navigation Compose.\",\n268:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-02-startup-session-navigation\"\n269:     },\n270:     {\n271:       \"sourceDependency\": \"androidx.datastore:datastore-preferences\",\n272:       \"replacementStrategy\": \"Replace with HarmonyOS-compatible preferences/storage service for persisted login state.\",\n273:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-02-startup-session-navigation\"\n274:     },\n275:     {\n276:       \"sourceDependency\": \"com.google.accompanist:accompanist-pager\",\n277:       \"replacementStrategy\": \"Replace with HarmonyOS pager/swiper equivalent or custom lightweight pager behavior for onboarding and history tabs.\",\n278:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-03-onboarding-login\"\n279:     },\n280:     {\n281:       \"sourceDependency\": \"com.google.dagger:hilt-android\",\n282:       \"replacementStrategy\": \"Use idiomatic Cangjie composition/service wiring rather than Android Hilt injection APIs.\",\n283:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-02-startup-session-navigation\"\n284:     },\n285:     {\n286:       \"sourceDependency\": \"androidx.core:core-splashscreen\",\n287:       \"replacementStrategy\": \"Use HarmonyOS startup page/loading gate behavior around persisted session lookup.\",\n288:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-02-startup-session-navigation\"\n289:     }\n290:   ],\n291:   \"tests\": [\n292:     {\n293:       \"name\": \"source-example-unit-test\",\n294:       \"sourcePaths\": [\n295:         \"app/src/test/java/com/example/foodike/ExampleUnitTest.kt\"\n296:       ],\n297:       \"strategy\": \"Do not migrate as meaningful business coverage; replace with focused target tests for actual app behavior.\",\n298:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-06-profile-capabilities-verification\",\n299:       \"commands\": []\n300:     },\n301:     {\n302:       \"name\": \"source-example-instrumented-test\",\n303:       \"sourcePaths\": [\n304:         \"app/src/androidTest/java/com/example/foodike/ExampleInstrumentedTest.kt\"\n305:       ],\n306:       \"strategy\": \"Do not rely on package-name smoke test; replace with focused target-side verification and manual route smoke where harness is limited.\",\n307:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-06-profile-capabilities-verification\",\n308:       \"commands\": []\n309:     },\n310:     {\n311:       \"name\": \"startup-session-tests\",\n312:       \"sourcePaths\": [\n313:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/common/SplashViewModel.kt\",\n314:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/data/repository/LoginRepositoryImpl.kt\"\n315:       ],\n316:       \"strategy\": \"Add focused target tests for start destination selection and persisted session toggling.\",\n317:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-02-startup-session-navigation\",\n318:       \"commands\": [\n319:         \"cjpm test\"\n320:       ]\n321:     },\n322:     {\n323:       \"name\": \"login-validation-tests\",\n324:       \"sourcePaths\": [\n325:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/login/LoginViewModel.kt\"\n326:       ],\n327:       \"strategy\": \"Add focused target tests for accepted credentials, rejected credentials, and emitted error state/snackbar model.\",\n328:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-03-onboarding-login\",\n329:       \"commands\": [\n330:         \"cjpm test\"\n331:       ]\n332:     },\n333:     {\n334:       \"name\": \"repository-refresh-tests\",\n335:       \"sourcePaths\": [\n336:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/data/repository/HomeRepositoryImpl.kt\",\n337:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/data/repository/UserDataRepositoryImpl.kt\"\n338:       ],\n339:       \"strategy\": \"Add focused target tests for selected restaurant propagation, menu retrieval, liked restaurant stream refresh, and cart item read behavior.\",\n340:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-04-home-history\",\n341:       \"commands\": [\n342:         \"cjpm test\"\n343:       ]\n344:     },\n345:     {\n346:       \"name\": \"detail-cart-state-tests\",\n347:       \"sourcePaths\": [\n348:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/details/RestaurantDetailViewModel.kt\",\n349:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/details/DetailScreenState.kt\",\n350:         \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/cart/Cart.kt\"\n351:       ],\n352:       \"strategy\": \"Add focused target tests for section toggles, menu partitioning, cart visibility rules, and summary helpers.\",\n353:       \"ownerPhase\": \"phase-05-detail-cart\",\n354:       \"commands\": [\n355:         \"cjpm test\"\n356:       ]\n357:     }\n358:   ],\n359:   \"phases\": [\n360:     {\n361:       \"id\": \"phase-01-project-skeleton-resources\",\n362:       \"title\": \"Project skeleton and resources\",\n363:       \"priority\": \"critical\",\n364:       \"targetScope\": [\n365:         \"Stabilize root app shell and route map.\",\n366:         \"Raise string/color/media resource parity before behavior-heavy phases.\",\n367:         \"Prevent broad shell files from absorbing unrelated future behavior.\"\n368:       ],\n369:       \"sourceEvidence\": [\n370:         \"app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml\",\n371:         \"app/src/main/res/values/strings.xml\",\n372:         \"app/src/main/res/values/colors.xml\",\n373:         \"app/src/main/res/values/themes.xml\",\n374:         \"README.md\",\n375:         \"translation-inputs/resource-coverage-report.md\",\n376:         \"translation-inputs/target-structure-report.md\"\n377:       ],\n378:       \"requiredInputs\": [\n379:         \"translation-inputs/plan-seed.md\",\n380:         \"translation-inputs/source-feature-survey.md\",\n381:         \"translation-inputs/resource-coverage-report.md\",\n382:         \"translation-inputs/target-structure-report.md\"\n383:       ],\n384:       \"expectedFiles\": [\n385:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj\",\n386:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/common/foodike_resources.cj\",\n387:         \"entry/src/main/resources/base/element/string.json\",\n388:         \"entry/src/main/resources/base/element/color.json\",\n389:         \"entry/src/main/resources/base/media\"\n390:       ],\n391:       \"gateCommand\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Sieger\\\\AppData\\\\Local\\\\Programs\\\\Python\\\\Python312\\\\python.exe D:\\\\X2Cangjie\\\\X2Cangjie\\\\scripts\\\\shared\\\\reports\\\\build_hap_report.py --workspace-root D:\\\\workspace\\\\Foodike --target-project D:\\\\workspace\\\\Foodike\\\\Foodike-Harmony --phase phase-01-project-skeleton-resources\",\n392:       \"expectedTests\": [\n393:         \"resource key/manual review of migrated strings and media references\"\n394:       ],\n395:       \"stateDataBehavior\": [\n396:         \"Route ids and screen titles must stay resource-backed.\",\n397:         \"Shell pages should stay thin so later state/data modules own business behavior.\"\n398:       ],\n399:       \"deferredRisks\": [\n400:         \"String/media parity remains incomplete if phase 01 is rushed.\",\n\n(Showing lines 1-400 of 1265. Use offset=401 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"files\": [\n    {\n      \"targetPath\": \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj\",\n      \"sourceReferences\": [\n        \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/MainActivity.kt\",\n        \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/util/Navigation.kt\"\n      ],\n      \"topLevelDefinitions\": [\n        \"bootstrap page shell\",\n        \"root route composition\"\n      ],\n      \"translationGuidelines\": [\n        \"Keep this file as a shell that delegates to feature modules.\",\n        \"Do not absorb repository or screen-specific logic here.\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"targetPath\": \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj\",\n      \"sourceReferences\": [","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"plan.json","time":{"start":1782526524929,"end":1782526524935}},"id":"prt_f06dc3df6001iN3uMgNGc7APKr","sessionID":"ses_0f923eeffffeBaDzycyPMFxg4Q","messageID":"msg_f06dc2d7700192wU8sQIW2WtJw"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782526524985,"sessionID":"ses_0f923eeffffeBaDzycyPMFxg4Q","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_DtCFED5OI1YLGhtOGUs3bPAp","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\docs\\harmonyos-cangjie-translation-checklist.md","limit":400},"output":"<path>D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\docs\\harmonyos-cangjie-translation-checklist.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # HarmonyOS Cangjie Translation Checklist\n2: \n3: 面向 Android Java app 迁移到 HarmonyOS Cangjie 的阶段性检查表。它来自 Spendee 案例记录和后续构建修复经验，目标是在每个 `opencode-cj` phase 结束时先抓住高频编译/宏展开问题，再进入下一阶段。\n4: \n5: ## 使用时机\n6: \n7: 1. 每个翻译 phase 开始前，把本 phase 可能触及的条目加入 `opencode-cj` prompt。\n8: 2. 每个 phase 结束后，先运行完整构建门禁：\n9: \n10:    `<python>` 表示当前 Python 解释器：macOS/Linux 可用 `python3`，Windows 可用 `py -3` 或 `python`。\n11: \n12:    ```bash\n13:    <python> scripts/shared/reports/build_hap_report.py \\\n14:      --workspace-root <translation-workspace> \\\n15:      --target-project <target-project> \\\n16:      --phase <phase-name>\n17:    ```\n18: \n19: 3. 如果报告失败，把 `build-reports/<phase-name>/build-report.md` 和首个 blocker 交给 `opencode-cj` 修复当前 phase，不要先开启下一阶段。\n20: 4. 构建通过后，再进入运行时 smoke 或行为验证。\n21: \n22: ## 资源和字符串边界\n23: \n24: - 不要把 `@r(...)` / `AppResource` 直接当作普通 `String`。\n25: - UI prop 如果可能接收资源字符串，优先使用 `ResourceStr`，或在边界处做 SDK 支持的显式转换。\n26: - 不要对 `ResourceStr` 调用普通字符串方法，例如 `isEmpty()`；需要空态时使用独立 `Bool` 状态。\n27: - 迁移 Android `setText(...)` 时，确认 HarmonyOS 端有明确的状态赋值或可观察数据源驱动文本刷新。\n28: - 每次资源迁移后，检查 `string.json`、media 资源和实际 UI 引用，避免保留旧 placeholder key 或缺失 AppScope/entry 双层资源。\n29: \n30: ## Option 和控制流\n31: \n32: - 不要生成 Java/Kotlin 风格的 `Option.get()`。\n33: - 非 UI helper 中使用 `match`、显式 `case Some(...)` / `case None`，或当前 SDK 支持的安全访问 API。\n34: - UI 构建逻辑中避免直接让 `match` 分支裸露生成不兼容的 component 形态；需要时拆成命名 `@Builder`。\n35: - 启动/依赖注入状态建议拆成明确的 `Bool`、错误资源、服务 option 解包 helper，减少 `@Component` 宏失败面。\n36: \n37: ## 包结构和导入\n38: \n39: - 避免 root package 与 `pages` / `routing` 之间出现环形依赖。公共 route 类型优先放在 `routing` 或独立 models/helpers 包。\n40: - UI 文件中避免宽泛 `std.collection.*` 导入；它可能和 ArkUI 组件名冲突，例如 `Stack`。\n41: - 需要集合类型时优先显式导入或限定命名。\n42: - helper 类型如果会通过 public `@Component` 生成构造器暴露，确认类型本身也是必要的 public 可见性。\n43: - 不要把临时 template/cache 文件当成迁移输入；`.cache`、build output 和 diagnostic log 只作为诊断证据。\n44: \n45: ## ArkUI Component 和 Builder\n46: \n47: - `@BuilderParam` 优先传入命名 `@Builder` 方法，不要依赖未验证的 inline closure 或 trailing component block。\n48: - 自定义容器组件要按当前 SDK 支持的构造器/slot 形态实现，不能照搬 ArkTS 示例。\n49: - 校验 ArkUI named arguments 和 modifiers 来自当前 Cangjie HarmonyOS SDK 文档，而不是只参考 ArkTS。\n50: - 对 `@Component` macro 失败，先缩小到入口组件状态、构造器 public 类型、资源字符串类型和 `@Publish` 字段类型这四类高频根因。\n51: - 组件内部紧密相关的 owner state 文本可直接在 owning page builder 中渲染，避免子组件 prop 复用导致同会话文本不刷新。\n52: \n53: ## 状态和可观察集合\n54: \n55: - 路由和跨页面状态模型使用 SDK 支持的 `@Observed`、`@Publish` 和明确字段类型。\n56: - 需要列表变化驱动 UI 时，使用 `ObservedArrayList` 等 SDK 支持的数据源，并给 `ForEach` 提供稳定 key。\n57: - 不要假设 `ObservedArrayList` 是普通 iterator；辅助逻辑中用下标访问或 SDK 支持方法。\n58: - 跨组件变化的 prop 需要 `@Prop` / `@Link` / `@Watch` 等明确同步链路。\n59: - 对 primitive totals、余额、计数等关键展示值，保存/编辑/删除成功后优先执行明确赋值，避免只依赖持久化回读触发 UI。\n60: \n61: ## 测试迁移和验证\n62: \n63: - 源项目已有测试时，当前 phase 相关测试应迁移或改写为目标侧测试，验证翻译后的业务、数据、状态、资源或刷新行为。\n64: - 源项目没有测试时，应为核心可测试逻辑补充适量测试；源测试过少时，应优先补高风险行为测试。\n65: - 如果当前 SDK/模板不支持某类自动化测试，应保持代码可测试，并记录 deferred validation、替代验证方法和后续完成路径。\n66: - 不要为了通过构建直接删除、禁用或弱化已迁移/生成的测试；应修实现、修测试集成，或明确记录当前阶段测试限制。\n67: \n68: ## 构建配置和工具链\n69: \n70: - 完整 HAP 构建必须使用 DevEco Cangjie plugin 管理的 full SDK，例如 `~/.cangjie-sdk/<version>/cangjie`；standalone `~/.local/cangjie` 只能代表轻量 `cjc` / `cjpm` 可用。\n71: - 缺少 full SDK 时，应先安装/启用 DevEco Studio Cangjie plugin，再继续 full build gate。\n72: - 每阶段记录构建命令、失败阶段、首个 blocker 和已解决 blocker。\n73: - 常见阶段含义：\n74:   - `ohpm install`：依赖、registry、模板测试依赖或 oh-package 问题。\n75:   - `SyncCangjieResource`：资源生成、配置 schema、Cangjie build support 注入问题。\n76:   - `CompileCangjie`：Cangjie 语法、宏展开、包依赖、ArkUI API 问题。\n77:   - `PackageHap`：资源/loader/package 产物问题。\n78:   - `SignHap`：签名配置问题；未签名 debug HAP 通常可能只是 warning。\n79: - full build 通过前，不要把 standalone `cjpm check` 失败简单等同于 HAP 构建失败；两者依赖来源不同。\n80: \n81: ## opencode-cj 修复交接\n82: \n83: - `apply_patch` 失败后必须 read-back，因为失败可能部分落盘。\n84: - `L.map is not a function`、`apply_patch verification failed`、`Failed to read file to update` 要分开记录。\n85: - 长 phase 被打断或恢复时，先让 `opencode-cj` 检查文件系统当前状态，再继续，不要重复生成同名组件或服务。\n86: - 构建 blocker prompt 应包含：\n87:   - 当前 phase 名称。\n88:   - `build-report.md` 路径。\n89:   - 失败阶段。\n90:   - 首个 blocker message 和 location。\n91:   - 只修当前 phase blocker 的约束。\n92: \n93: ## Phase Gate 验收\n94: \n95: - `build_hap_report.py` 的 Markdown/JSON 报告存在。\n96: - 报告包含 command、result、failed stage、first blocker、warnings、HAP artifacts。\n97: - 如果失败，已有 `opencode-build-blocker-prompt.txt` 可直接交给 `opencode-cj`。\n98: - 如果成功，报告记录 full build gate 通过，且可把本 phase 的已知编译 blocker 标为 resolved。\n99: - 下一 phase 只能在构建通过，或用户明确批准带 blocker 继续时开始。\n100: \n101: ## Spendee 证据映射\n102: \n103: - `@r(...)` / `ResourceStr` 误用导致重复 generic inference 和 macro blocker。\n104: - `Option.get()` 在当前 SDK 下不可用，入口和服务解包需改为显式 `match`。\n105: - root/pages/routing 包循环会阻断 `CompileCangjie`。\n106: - UI 文件中的 `std.collection.*` 与 ArkUI `Stack` 名称冲突。\n107: - `@BuilderParam` 命名 builder 比 inline closure 更稳定。\n108: - `ObservedArrayList` 不能按普通 `for-in` 假设处理。\n109: - 同会话 finance totals 刷新最终需要 owner state、显式赋值和可观察列表配合，构建通过不能替代运行时刷新验证。\n110: - 如果 full SDK 在 Phase 1 就接入，许多 Cangjie/ArkUI 编译问题可以在引入当 phase 就暴露，而不是累积到最终构建。\n\n(End of file - total 110 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# HarmonyOS Cangjie Translation Checklist\n\n面向 Android Java app 迁移到 HarmonyOS Cangjie 的阶段性检查表。它来自 Spendee 案例记录和后续构建修复经验，目标是在每个 `opencode-cj` phase 结束时先抓住高频编译/宏展开问题，再进入下一阶段。\n\n## 使用时机\n\n1. 每个翻译 phase 开始前，把本 phase 可能触及的条目加入 `opencode-cj` prompt。\n2. 每个 phase 结束后，先运行完整构建门禁：\n\n   `<python>` 表示当前 Python 解释器：macOS/Linux 可用 `python3`，Windows 可用 `py -3` 或 `python`。\n\n   ```bash\n   <python> scripts/shared/reports/build_hap_report.py \\\n     --workspace-root <translation-workspace> \\\n     --target-project <target-project> \\\n     --phase <phase-name>\n   ```\n\n3. 如果报告失败，把 `build-reports/<phase-name>/build-report.md` 和首个 blocker 交给 `opencode-cj` 修复当前 phase，不要先开启下一阶段。\n4. 构建通过后，再进入运行时 smoke 或行为验证。","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"..\\..\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\docs\\harmonyos-cangjie-translation-checklist.md","time":{"start":1782526524955,"end":1782526524984}},"id":"prt_f06dc3e03001FxK2j93kSYRtZ6","sessionID":"ses_0f923eeffffeBaDzycyPMFxg4Q","messageID":"msg_f06dc2d7700192wU8sQIW2WtJw"}}
