 of data conversion and string formatting. It acts as a practical guide for developers who need to bridge the gap between raw string data and strongly typed system values. The content focuses on utilizing the `format` method for precise output control—such as alignment and width—and the `convert` module for parsing strings into Integers, Floats, and Booleans. This collection is highly suitable for Cangjie programmers aiming to master data validation, handle user input securely, and ensure clean, formatted output in their applications. By understanding these core utilities, developers can write more robust, error-resistant code that handles real-world data scenarios effectively, ultimately improving application stability and user experience.\",\r\n      \"paths\": [\r\n        \"std/convert_samples/.abstract.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"source\": \"std\",\r\n      \"doc_kind\": \"abstract\"\r\n    }\r\n  ],\r\n  \"paths\": [\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkinterop/cj-apis-ark_interop/ohosark_interopArkTS互操作库/class_JSContext/func_stringUtf16S_3more_2277e591.md\",\r\n    \"std/time_package_structs/结构体/struct_DateTime/func_formatString_6more.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-information-display-alphabetindexer/AlphabetIndexer/组件属性/func_selectedFont_2more_09e81d48.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-image-video-image/Image/组件属性/func_altResourceS_7more_c131e412.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkinterop/cj-apis-ark_interop/ohosark_interopArkTS互操作库/class_JSContext/func_requireArkMo_3more_f355f2ec.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-dialog-alertdialog/警告弹窗AlertDialog/class_AlertDialogParam/initResourceStr_ResourceStr_ResourceStr_B_1361bb41/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-dialog-alertdialog/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-dialog-alertdialog/警告弹窗AlertDialog/.overview.md\",\r\n    \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-dialog-alertdialog/警告弹窗AlertDialog/class_AlertDialogButtonBaseOptions/