: \n67: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.Global.ResourceManager\n68: \n69: **起始版本：** 22\n70: \n71: ### var id\n72: \n73: ```cangjie\n74: public var id: UInt32\n75: ```\n76: \n77: **功能：** 资源的id值。\n78: \n79: **类型：** UInt32\n80: \n81: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.Global.ResourceManager\n82: \n83: **起始版本：** 22\n84: \n85: ### var moduleName\n86: \n87: ```cangjie\n88: public var moduleName: String\n89: ```\n90: \n91: **功能：** 应用的module名称。\n92: \n93: **类型：** String\n94: \n95: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.Global.ResourceManager\n96: \n97: **起始版本：** 22\n98: \n99: ### var params\n100: \n101: ```cangjie\n102: public var params:?Array<Any>\n103: ```\n104: \n105: **功能：** 其他资源参数，包括资源名、格式化接口的替换值、复数接口的量词。\n106: \n107: **类型：** ?Array\\<Any>\n108: \n109: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.Global.ResourceManager\n110: \n111: **起始版本：** 22\n112: \n113: ### var resType\n114: \n115: ```cangjie\n116: public var resType:?Int32\n117: ```\n118: \n119: **功能：** 资源的类型。\n120: \n121: **类型：** ?Int32\n122: \n123: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.Global.ResourceManager\n124: \n125: **起始版本：** 22\n126: \n127: ### init(String, String, UInt32, ?Array\\<Any>, ?Int32)\n128: \n129: ```cangjie\n130: public init(\n131:     bundleName: String,\n132:     moduleName: String,\n133:     id: UInt32,\n134:     params!: ?Array<Any> = None,\n135:     resType!: ?Int32 = None\n136: )\n137: ```\n138: \n139: **功能：** 构造资源类型对象。\n140: \n141: **系统能力：** SystemCapability.Global.ResourceManager\n142: \n143: **起始版本：** 22\n144: \n145: **参数：**\n146: \n147: |参数名|类型|必填|默认值|说明|\n148: |:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n149: |bundleName|String|是|-|应用的bundle名称。|\n150: |moduleName|String|是|-|应用的module名称。|\n151: |id|UInt32|是|-|资源的id值。|\n152: |params|?Array\\<Any>|否|None| **命名参数。** 其他资源参数，包括资源名、格式化接口的替换值、复数接口的量词。|\n153: |resType|?Int32|否|None| **命名参数。** 资源的类型。|\n\n(End of file - total 153 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# ohos.resource\n\n<!--Del-->\n> **说明：**\n>\n> 当前为Beta阶段。\n<!--DelEnd-->\n\nresource模块描述资源类型。\n\n## 导入模块\n\n```cangjie\nimport kit.LocalizationKit.*\n```\n\n## 使用说明\n\nAPI示例代码使用说明：\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\LocalizationKit\\cj-apis-resource\\cj-apis-resource.md","time":{"start":1782526579718,"end":1782526579730}},"id":"prt_f06dd1399001pA3bbSNlfR0Die","sessionID":"ses_0f923eeffffeBaDzycyPMFxg4Q","messageID":"msg_f06dcd738001qhx1NmsyxBtfCM"}}
