{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782526638664,"sessionID":"ses_0f923eeffffeBaDzycyPMFxg4Q","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_j3i6cRHBOzchN3XGR3DAGTRG","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"Test-Path -LiteralPath \"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\"; if ($?) { $patch = @'\n{\n  \"schemaVersion\": 1,\n  \"purpose\": \"Resolve phase-01 localization-resources with direct Cangjie resource APIs.\",\n  \"updates\": [\n    {\n      \"capabilityId\": \"localization-resources\",\n      \"set\": {\n        \"status\": \"verified-direct\",\n        \"targetCapabilitySearch\": [\n          \"Cangjie SDK declarations confirm direct resource support in pure Cangjie: `ohos.base.ResourceStr` (`C:\\\\Users\\\\Sieger\\\\.cangjie-sdk\\\\6.0\\\\cangjie\\\\api\\\\modules\\\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\\\ohos\\\\ohos.base.cj.d:618-626`), `ohos.resource.AppResource` (`...\\\\ohos.resource.cj.d:20-97`), and `ohos.resource_manager.ResourceManager` formatted string APIs including `getString`, `getStringByName`, `getPluralStringByName`, and numeric lookups (`...\\\\ohos.resource_manager.cj.d:20-199`).\",\n          \"HarmonyOS Cangjie docs confirm `ohos.resource` is a Cangjie-callable LocalizationKit module imported via `import kit.LocalizationKit.*`, and `AppResource` carries bundle/module/id plus formatting params for resource lookup (`D:\\\\workspace\\\\Foodike\\\\.agents\\\\skills\\\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\\\API\\\\LocalizationKit\\\\cj-apis-resource\\\\cj-apis-resource.md:9-153`).\",\n          \"HarmonyOS resource guidance confirms the standard HarmonyOS resource-category and access path should be used for multi-language and multi-device adaptation rather than custom fallback handling (`D:\\\\workspace\\\\Foodike\\\\.agents\\\\skills\\\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\\\Guide\\\\cj-start\\\\start\\\\cj-ide-resource-categories-and-access\\\\资源分类与访问\\\\.abstract.md:1`).\"\n        ],\n        \"targetApiOrLibrary\": \"HarmonyOS Cangjie LocalizationKit resource model (`ohos.base.ResourceStr`, `ohos.resource.AppResource`, `ohos.resource_manager.ResourceManager`) with standard HarmonyOS `string.json`/`color.json` resources\",\n        \"targetStrategy\": \"Phase 01 should migrate Android strings/colors/themes/media into HarmonyOS resource files and keep user-visible labels resource-backed. Use `ResourceStr`/`AppResource` directly in ArkUI component props where supported, and use `ResourceManager.getString(...)` / `getStringByName(...)` for formatted or named retrieval instead of hard-coded strings or local fallback tables.\",\n        \"targetEndpoints\": [\n          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj\",\n          \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/common/foodike_resources.cj\",\n          \"entry/src/main/resources/base/element/string.json\",\n          \"entry/src/main/resources/base/element/color.json\"\n        ],\n        \"tests\": [\n          \"string key coverage check\",\n          \"placeholder preservation check\",\n          \"locale selection smoke test\"\n        ],\n        \"sdkDeclarationEvidence\": [\n          \"`ohos.base.ResourceStr` is a direct SDK interface and `String` extends it (`C:\\\\Users\\\\Sieger\\\\.cangjie-sdk\\\\6.0\\\\cangjie\\\\api\\\\modules\\\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\\\ohos\\\\ohos.base.cj.d:618-626`).\",\n          \"`ohos.resource.AppResource` directly implements `ResourceStr` and carries `params` for formatted resource usage (`C:\\\\Users\\\\Sieger\\\\.cangjie-sdk\\\\6.0\\\\cangjie\\\\api\\\\modules\\\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\\\ohos\\\\ohos.resource.cj.d:20-97`).\",\n          \"`ohos.resource_manager.ResourceManager` exposes direct Cangjie string/number/plural retrieval APIs including formatted lookups (`C:\\\\Users\\\\Sieger\\\\.cangjie-sdk\\\\6.0\\\\cangjie\\\\api\\\\modules\\\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\\\ohos\\\\ohos.resource_manager.cj.d:20-199`).\",\n          \"ArkUI components consume resource-backed values directly, for example `Text.init(content: ?ResourceStr, ...)` (`C:\\\\Users\\\\Sieger\\\\.cangjie-sdk\\\\6.0\\\\cangjie\\\\api\\\\modules\\\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\\\ohos\\\\ohos.arkui.component.text.cj.d:47-59`) and `Button.init(label: ResourceStr)` (`C:\\\\Users\\\\Sieger\\\\.cangjie-sdk\\\\6.0\\\\cangjie\\\\api\\\\modules\\\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\\\ohos\\\\ohos.arkui.component.button.cj.d:306-314`).\"\n        ],\n        \"cangjieCallableEvidence\": [\n          \"LocalizationKit documentation defines `ohos.resource` as a Cangjie module imported with `import kit.LocalizationKit.*`, with `AppResource` available to Cangjie code (`D:\\\\workspace\\\\Foodike\\\\.agents\\\\skills\\\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\\\API\\\\LocalizationKit\\\\cj-apis-resource\\\\cj-apis-resource.md:9-153`).\",\n          \"The installed SDK declarations plus ArkUI `ResourceStr` component signatures provide a direct Cangjie-callable path for localized labels and formatted resources without introducing an ArkTS bridge.\"\n        ],\n        \"discoveryOnlyEvidence\": [],\n        \"compileProbeEvidence\": [],\n        \"preResolutionDecision\": \"resolved-real-api\",\n        \"phaseCapabilityResolution\": \"resolved-real-api\",\n        \"blocker\": \"\",\n        \"targetFallback\": \"\",\n        \"futureCompletionPath\": \"\",\n        \"notes\": \"Direct Cangjie resource APIs exist, so this capability must be implemented in phase 01 through real HarmonyOS resource files and resource-backed UI text. No package lookup or bridge is needed for this phase capability.\",\n        \"capabilityFacts\": {\n          \"schemaVersion\": 1,\n          \"resolutionKind\": \"direct-api\",\n          \"activeFallback\": {\n            \"used\": false,\n            \"fallbackKind\": \"\",\n            \"reason\": \"\",\n            \"blocker\": \"\"\n          },\n          \"apiEvidence\": [\n            {\n             