mentation using the resolved direct resource path.\n\nResolved capabilities:\n- `localization-resources` -> `resolved-real-api`\n\nReal APIs/packages found:\n- Direct Cangjie SDK resource model, no extra package needed.\n- `ohos.base.ResourceStr`\n- `ohos.resource.AppResource`\n- `ohos.resource_manager.ResourceManager`\n- ArkUI components that directly accept `ResourceStr`, including:\n  - `Text.init(content: ?ResourceStr, ...)`\n  - `Button.init(label: ResourceStr)`\n\nKey evidence used:\n- `C:\\Users\\Sieger\\.cangjie-sdk\\6.0\\cangjie\\api\\modules\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\ohos\\ohos.base.cj.d:618-626`\n- `C:\\Users\\Sieger\\.cangjie-sdk\\6.0\\cangjie\\api\\modules\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\ohos\\ohos.resource.cj.d:20-97`\n- `C:\\Users\\Sieger\\.cangjie-sdk\\6.0\\cangjie\\api\\modules\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\ohos\\ohos.resource_manager.cj.d:20-199`\n- `C:\\Users\\Sieger\\.cangjie-sdk\\6.0\\cangjie\\api\\modules\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\ohos\\ohos.arkui.component.text.cj.d:47-59`\n- `C:\\Users\\Sieger\\.cangjie-sdk\\6.0\\cangjie\\api\\modules\\linux_ohos_aarch64_cjnative\\ohos\\ohos.arkui.component.button.cj.d:306-314`\n- `D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\API\\LocalizationKit\\cj-apis-resource\\cj-apis-resource.md:9-153`\n\nGenuinely blocked capabilities:\n- none for this phase\n- other unresolved capabilities remain in later phases, but they are out of scope for `phase-01-project-skeleton-resources`\n\nWhether phase implementation may begin:\n- Yes. The only current-phase critical/high platform capability is now resolved in the authority record.\n- The generated `phase-capability-checklist.md` still shows the old unresolved snapshot, but the source of truth `platform-capability-check.json/md` is updated correctly.","time":{"start":1782526720614,"end":1782526726683}}}
